Package org.opt4j.satdecoding

Class VarOrder

java.lang.Object
org.opt4j.satdecoding.Order
org.opt4j.satdecoding.VarOrder
public class VarOrder extends Order
The VarOrder implements an Order like it is used in MiniSAT. Each variable has an activity and a prioritized decision phase.
